-- out/todo.txt --
issue3750.original: v3 has more complex nested disjunction structure in sub field; v2 resolves to concrete value.
issue3750.reduced: v3 has different field ordering in disjunction sub-fields compared to v2.
issue3780.panic1: v3 error message is "required field missing: param"; v2 is "incomplete bool: bool".
